                "invention-title": [
                    "Multi-pollutant flue gas treatment method",
                    "一种多污染物烟气的处理方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "An existing flue gas purification process is improved and optimized, the denitration tower is designed to be of a multi-chamber structure, activated carbon with the high ammonium chloride content in the front chamber of the denitration tower is directly fed into the desorption tower to be regenerated or enters the dechlorination tower to be dechlorinated, and only activated carbon in the middle chamber and the rear chamber of the denitration tower is fed into the desulfurization tower; the hydrogen chloride is effectively prevented from being enriched in the system or damaging downstream process equipment. Meanwhile, the mass of activated carbon circulating in the system and the usage amount of ammonia gas and sulfur dioxide are calculated according to the content of pollutants in the flue gas, real-time adjustment is conducted according to detection and calculation results, material waste is prevented, the operation cost of the system is saved, and efficient and low-cost removal of SO2, NOx and HCl is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明对现有烟气净化工艺做出改进优化，将脱硝塔设计为多仓室结构，并将脱硝塔前室中氯化铵含量较高的活性炭直接送入解析塔再生或进入脱氯塔脱氯，仅将脱硝塔中室、后室的活性炭送入脱硫塔，有效防止了氯化氢在系统内部富集或对下游工艺设备造成危害。同时根据烟气中各污染物的含量，计算系统中循环的活性炭质量，以及氨气、二氧化硫的使用量，根据检测和计算结果实时调整，防止物料浪费，节约了系统的运行成本，实现SO2、NOx、HCl的高效、低成本脱除。"
                }
            ]
